<ab>Dem edeln und vesten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>,
                        hofmeister auff Tyröl und hauptman an der Etsche </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt etlich
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und kauffleute, wie in etwievil habe und
                        kauffmanschaft in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ichs</ex></expan> von
                        Osterreich <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>herschäft<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>gepiete<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und <add>etlich die
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dabey</add> bekumert sey
                                <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
                        ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dinste
                            <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gen
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        beweysen wöllet, daz in dieselb ir hab und
                            <expan>kauffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan> wider und on hindernüsse volg und
                            <add>auch die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ledig </add>
<expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
